  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Cumulative Endpoint</measure>
    <time_frame>10 weeks</time_frame>
    <description>Improvement in at least one of these criteria without significant worsening in any of them. 1) improvement by 2 or more lines of best-corrected Snellen visual acuity in at least one eye; (2) reduction in dose of systemic corticosteroid or other immunosuppressive therapy by at least 50%; (3) two-step improvement in control of ocular inflammation; and (4) reduction of cystoid macular edema and other inflammatory signs on angiography.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Cumulative Endpoint</measure>
    <time_frame>50 Weeks</time_frame>
